<div type="abstract"><head>Heinrich d. J. Hutt, Bürger zu Nürnberg, an Heimeran Nothafft, Verweser in Niederbayern</head><p>Der Absender bittet um Ansetzung eines Gerichtstages mit Georg I. von Aichberg zu Söldenau bis Pfingsten, da dieser Ansprüche gegen Hutt vorbringt und sie sich beide zur Verhandlung des Streits vor dem Adressaten und anderen Räten zu Straubing bereit erklärt haben.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_423" id="210v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l25">Jdem hutt . <expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> heymram
                        Nothaft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l26"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>weſer</expan> in
                                <expan>Nıd<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Peyern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_423_r1l27"><expan>Erberg<ex>er</ex></expan> lıeber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . es meynt <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Görg <expan>Aıchperg<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu ſeldnaw . ettlıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l28">ſprüch ʒu mır ʒu <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> er <expan>meıne<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des Rats ʒu <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l29"><expan>geſchrıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd Jch den <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>heydenab<ex>er</ex></expan> nehſt ʒu Jm geſandt hett . der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l30">hat mir geſagt wıe er nach vıl rede von <expan>meine<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>aufgenome<ex>n</ex></expan> hab </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l31">daʒ ıch Jm von wıllkür eins <expan>freẅntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ſein ſülle <expan>hıeʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l32"><expan>pfıngſt<ex>en</ex></expan> ſchıerıſt vor <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> vnd den <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>mein<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> den Reͣten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l33">ʒu Strawbıng / Vnd wıe er ʒu Strawbıng <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ſey vnd eẅr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l34"><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan> wölt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> da weͣrt Jr niht anheim / Alſo geb Jm der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l35"><expan>lantſchr<ex>eiber</ex></expan> ʒu antwurt / Wenn wır <expan>beıd<ex>er</ex>ſeıt</expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> beͣten . ſo wurd man </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l36">vns tag <expan>ſecʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd der ſache mıt <expan>freẅntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> ein ent <expan>mache<ex>n</ex></expan> . Nu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l37">wıe wol ıch des niht pflıchtıg <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> vnd mır von <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> meins geſchefts </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l38"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> niht wol füklıch ıſt Doch ſo es der <expan>heydenab<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>aufgenom<ex>en</ex></expan> hat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l39">ſo wıl ıch dem <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Görg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Aıchperg<ex>er</ex></expan> . von wıllkür . <expan>freẅntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l40"><expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> alſo ſein . vor <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> vnd den <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>mein<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> den <expan>Reͣte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l41">ʒu Strawbıng / Vnd bıtt eẅr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> dıenſtlıch mıt fleıſſ . eẅch des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l42">ʒuuerfahen . Vnd vns des <expan>beıd<ex>er</ex>ſeıt</expan> auf dıe <expan>nehſtkünftıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>pfıngſt<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_424" id="211r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_424_r2l2"><expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıchen</expan> tag <expan>ʒuſecʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd mir den ſo ʒeıtlıch beuor <expan>ʒuv<ex>er</ex>künden</expan> . daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_424_r2l3">ıch den auch <expan>erlange<ex>n</ex></expan> mug . ſo wıl ıch des meins taıls niht ſeẅmıg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_424_r2l4">ſein on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> . Jch han auch dem <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>görg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>aıchperg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>geſchrıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_424_r2l5">eẅr <expan>erberk<ex>er</ex></expan> . auch ʒu <expan>bıtte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_424_r1l1"><expan>ecıa<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>addıc<ex>i</ex>o</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_424_r1l2">ın <expan>ſ<ex>e</ex>c<ex>un</ex>da</expan> <expan>lıtt<ex>er</ex>a</expan> </ab></add> Denn wo ıch <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>gedıene<ex>n</ex></expan> möcht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_424_r2l6">etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_423" id="210v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Idem Hutt, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Heymram Nothaft,
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>weser</expan> in <expan>Nid<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        Peyern</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Erberg<ex>er</ex></expan> lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, es
                        meynt <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Görg <expan>Aichperg<ex>er</ex></expan> zu
                        Seldnaw ettlich sprüch zu mir zu <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> er <expan>meine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des rats zu <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
<expan>geschribe<ex>n</ex></expan> und ich den <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Heydenab<ex>er</ex></expan> nehst zu im gesandt hett; der hat mir
                        gesagt, wie er nach vil rede von <expan>meine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>aufgenome<ex>n</ex></expan> hab, daz ich im von willkür eins
                                <expan>frewntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> sein sülle
                            <expan>hiezwisch<ex>en</ex></expan>
<app><note><q type="date"><expan>pfingst<ex>en</ex></expan> schierist</q>31.05.1422</note></app> vor
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> und den <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>mein<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> den reͣten zu Strawbing, und wie er zu
                        Strawbing <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> sey und ewr
                                <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan> wölt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, da
                        weͣrt ir niht anheim, also geb im der <expan>lantschr<ex>eiber</ex></expan>
                        zu antwurt, wenn wir <expan>beid<ex>er</ex>seit</expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> beͣten, so wurd man uns tag
                                <expan>secze<ex>n</ex></expan> und der sache mit
                                <expan>frewntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> ein ent <expan>mache<ex>n</ex></expan>. Nu
                        wie wol ich des niht pflichtig <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> und mir von
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> meins geschefts
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> niht wol füklich ist, doch so es der
                                <expan>Heydenab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>aufgenom<ex>en</ex></expan> hat, so wil ich dem
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Görg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Aichperg<ex>er</ex></expan> von willkür
                            <expan>frewntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> also sein vor <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> und den <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>mein<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> den <expan>reͣte<ex>n</ex></expan> zu
                        Strawbing, und bitt ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> dienstlich mit
                        fleiss, ewch des zu verfahen und uns des <expan>beid<ex>er</ex>seit</expan>
                        auf die <expan>nehstkünftig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>pfingst<ex>en</ex></expan>
<pb facs="#facs_424" id="211r"/>
<expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lichen</expan> tag <expan>zu secze<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        und mir den so zeitlich bevor <expan>zu v<ex>er</ex>künden</expan>, daz ich
                        den auch <expan>erlange<ex>n</ex></expan> mug, so wil ich des meins tails
                        niht sewmig sein on <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>. Ich han auch dem
                                <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Görg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Aichperg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>geschribe<ex>n</ex></expan> ewr <expan>erberk<ex>er</ex></expan> auch
                        zu <expan>bitte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><expan>ecia<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>addic<ex>i</ex>o</expan> in
                                <expan>s<ex>e</ex>c<ex>un</ex>da</expan>
<expan>litt<ex>er</ex>a</expan></add>. Denn wo ich
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>gediene<ex>n</ex></expan> möcht etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
